- `envoy.reloadable_features.grpc_side_stream_flow_control` — registered in `/workspace/envoy-v1.31/source/common/runtime/runtime_features.cc` at line 52, used in `/workspace/envoy-v1.31/source/extensions/filters/http/ext_proc/client_impl.h` and `.cc`, and tested with the flag set to `false` in the integration test at line 4544 of `ext_proc_integration_test.cc`.
